summary:
The starks at Disney land 
Ned: Robb where’s Arya? Sansa, Jon do you have on enough sunscreen-
Catelyn: Bran no! You’re not...
body:
The starks at Disney land

Ned: Robb where’s Arya? Sansa, Jon do you have on enough sunscreen-

Catelyn: Bran no! You’re not allowed to climb splash mountain!

Robb: *forced to ride its a Small world over and over by rickon*

Jon: went into the haunted mansion just to brood.

Sansa: walking around trying to glimps Gaston during the parade.

Arya: got lost in hidden kingdom and hasn’t been seen since, caught by Jon later talking to to the statue of Elizabeth Swan in the pirates of the Caribbean ride.

Bran: climbing splash mountain anyways

Rickon: still with Robb on “its a small world”

Discuss
